Get Headup Activation Angle Settings (0x32)
Send to the right arm.

Response

Get Glasses Serial Number Information (0x33)
Fetches the Serial number of the individual lens.

Response
Response is ASCII

Get Device Serial Number Information (0x34)
Fetched the Serial number of the Glasses.

Response
Response is ASCII


The serial number can be fetched from the BLE Scan Result object. For example:S110LAAL103842
The first 4 characters indicate the frame shape.


The next 3 characters indicate the color of the frames.

Get ESB Channel Information (0x35)
The two lenses communicate using ESB. This lists the ESB channel they are talking on.
0x35

0x35 0xc9 0x57 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00 0x00

