Set Dashboard Settings (0x06)
What are these?
sent status 06  L 0 , sent size: 7  sent: 06 07 00 9a 06 00 02 
sent status 06  R 0 , sent size: 7  sent: 06 07 00 9a 06 00 02 
sent status 06  L 0 , sent size: 22  sent: 06 16 00 9b 01 59 7e 48 68 a1 8c 2d 5b 97 01 00 00 ff ff 01 01 00 
sent status 06  R 0 , sent size: 22  sent: 06 16 00 9b 01 59 7e 48 68 a1 8c 2d 5b 97 01 00 00 ff ff 01 01 00 
sent status 06  L 0 , sent size: 12  sent: 06 0c 00 9c 03 01 00 01 00 00 02 01 
sent status 06  R 0 , sent size: 12  sent: 06 0c 00 9c 03 01 00 01 00 00 02 01 

Send settings to control the dashboard. The length includes full packet length, including the command, length, pad and sequence in addition to the payload. Subcommands are listed below with their payloads.

Set Time and Weather

Weather Icon IDs

Set Dashboard Mode
Set the dashboard mode, currently has three modes: minimal, dual, full

Dashboard Mode IDs

Secondary Pane IDs
Only respected on Full or Dual Mode

Response
The response repeats back the sequence 

